job_history.work_description: Assisted in the conduct of program orientations for large and small groups, complete individual mentoring of students, analyzed and synthesized data and information, wrote clear and concise reports, and effectively communicated with the staff, students and many members of a multidisciplinary team.

Trained and evaluated the organizational effectiveness of units using virtual or constructive simulations. Planned and conducted training exercises in support of Army National Guard and Reserve Component units preparing for movement overseas.

skills.name: Training and Development
skills.explanation: Has extensive experience in training and evaluating units using virtual or constructive simulations, and planning and conducting training exercises, showing strong proficiency.

skills.name: Leadership
skills.explanation: Trained and evaluated units, and planned and conducted training exercises, indicating a solid level of proficiency in leadership.

skills.name: Communication

skills.name: Data Analysis

skills.name: Mentoring
